title: Gannets
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, International, Organic, Buffet, Salad bar, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Family owned cafe in Georgian building near the castle. Uses locally sourced and organic ingredients. Aware of different dietary needs or choices. Staff friendly and helpful. No vegan dishes listed on menu but are available, as well as soya milk and dairy free spread. Inside and outdoor seating.
